WEBVTT

00:00.120 --> 00:03.028
They don't bring life but they are necessary for life.

00:04.179 --> 00:06.449
Earthquakes are a sign that the Earth is still alive.

00:06.551 --> 00:09.931
It's not a dead planet like the planet Mars, for example.

00:13.911 --> 00:17.673
And we need a planet to be alive to create landscapes.

00:18.271 --> 00:21.180
We will all be underwater if there were no mountains.

00:21.760 --> 00:28.196
And so despite the fact that they are a big hazard and that they bring destruction,...

00:28.684 --> 00:30.853
...without earthquakes we would all be dead.

